---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="HomeRecordingGear — Honest Gear for Beginner Producers"
  description="Honest, opinionated home recording gear recommendations for beginners spending $50–$300 on their first home studio. No fluff, no filler."
>
  <div class="space-y-12">
    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight">
        Home recording gear,<br />without the confusion.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
        I researched this so you don't have to. Honest, opinionated recommendations
        for beginners spending $50–$300 on their first home studio.
      </p>
    </div>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Best-of lists</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2">
        <li>
          <a href="/best-microphones-under-100" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-medium">
            Best microphones under $100
          </a>
          <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm ml-2">— The sweet spot for most beginners</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/best-audio-interfaces-for-beginners" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-medium">
            Best audio interfaces for beginners
          </a>
          <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm ml-2">— You need one if you want XLR</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/best-headphones-for-home-recording-under-100" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-medium">
            Best headphones for home recording under $100
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/best-home-recording-bundles-under-200" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-medium">
            Best home recording bundles under $200
          </a>
          <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm ml-2">— Just tell me what to buy</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/best-condenser-microphones-under-50" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-medium">
            Best condenser microphones under $50
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Head-to-head comparisons</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2">
        <li>
          <a href="/focusrite-scarlett-solo-vs-2i2" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-medium">
            Focusrite Scarlett Solo vs 2i2
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/blue-yeti-vs-shure-sm7b" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-medium">
            Blue Yeti vs Shure SM7B
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/usb-vs-xlr-microphone-beginners" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-medium">
            USB vs XLR microphone — which should beginners get?
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Start here</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2">
        <li>
          <a href="/how-to-set-up-a-home-recording-studio-on-a-budget" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-medium">
            How to set up a home recording studio on a budget
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/what-audio-interface-do-i-need" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-medium">
            What audio interface do I actually need?
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
